                     <interp inst="t17841208-1-off2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17841208-1-victim69" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Reed
