                  , between the hours of three and five in the afternoon, on the <rs id="t17841208-1-cd3" type="crimeDate">12th day of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17841208-1-off2 t17841208-1-cd3"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17841208-1-off10 t17841208-1-cd3"></join>
